snippet.title: Johnny Depp Vs Amber Heard // Case Delay #JusticeforJohnny
snippet.description:
In this video I talk about a variety of my opinions I have on this case with stuff that's been reported in the past few week. #JusticeforJohnny #Imanotbot

I'm still waiting on the verdict, shouldn't be much longer. That video will be in a different format. I am posting these videos for support and that I am not a bot so this isn't swept under the rug. 

Please sign the Remove Amber from Aquaman 2 petition. https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

Also check out the same channels I watch on this topic (they do better than me)
